pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers

Class ParentViewController

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.ParentViewController

  • public class ParentViewController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the controller for the "parent tab" that has:

    a table view parentTV, that displays the other parents that are part of the family of

    the logged parent, returned by the method:

    PersonDAO.getLoggedParent()

    a "plus button" that opens the "add parent window", managed by:

    pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.AddParentController.java

    a "notifications button" that opens the "notifications window" managed by:

    pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.NotificationsController.java

    buttons to the other tabs: kids, tasks and rewards:

    pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.KidViewController.java

    pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.TaskViewController.java

    pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.RewardViewController.java

    The "parent tab" is in this fxml file: pt.iade.ManageeMHome.views#parentView.fxml.

    Author:
    jaime
